    <item>
      <title>国际货币基金组织致电补贴削减后，安哥拉远足柴油价格50％</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/angola-hikes-diesel-prices-50-after-imf-call-for-subsidy-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[安哥拉将柴油价格提高了50％，这是一个长期以来居民一直在努力应对生活成本增加的国家的第二次上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/angola-hikes-diesel-prices-50-after-imf-call-for-subsidy-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 12:39:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥通货膨胀率在Banixo投票之前的预测远远超过预测</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/mexico-inflation-slows-more-than-forecast-before-banxico-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥的通货膨胀率在3月上半年的预期速度比预期的要快，因为中央银行将在本周开会，以考虑连续第六次降低速度，并可能连续第二次降低一半。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/mexico-inflation-slows-more-than-forecast-before-banxico-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 12:31:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伦敦房屋价格更便宜，但仍然无法承受</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/london-house-prices-become-cheaper-but-are-still-unaffordable</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伦敦的房屋是他们十年来最实惠的房屋，但对于许多人来说仍然是遥不可及的，强调了工党政府在解决英国住房危机方面面临的挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/london-house-prices-become-cheaper-but-are-still-unaffordable</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 12:04:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国确认2Q债务发行，将重新引入7年债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/germany-confirms-second-quarter-debt-issuance-of-92-5-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国金融机构确认，第二季度将出售925亿欧元（1000亿美元）的联邦政府债务，并宣布计划在下半年重新引入7年债券的销售。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/germany-confirms-second-quarter-debt-issuance-of-92-5-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 09:00:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卡尼警告特朗普“想打破我们”，加拿大高风险开始</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/carney-warns-trump-wants-to-break-us-as-high-stakes-canadian-election-begins</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马克·卡尼（Mark Carney）开始竞标选举，并警告说，美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）认真对待想要吞并加拿大的努力，以说服加拿大人他可以保护该国免受美国侵略。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/carney-warns-trump-wants-to-break-us-as-high-stakes-canadian-election-begins</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 02:46:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纳米比亚的新总统名字代理，修剪机柜</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-22/namibia-s-new-president-names-witbooi-as-deputy-trims-cabinet</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纳米比亚总统Netumbo Nandi-Ndaitwah任命了长期服务的议员Lucia Witbooi为她的副手，因为她揭露了一个精简的内阁，巩固了关键的部门，并将石油和天然气放在自己的办公室下。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-22/namibia-s-new-president-names-witbooi-as-deputy-trims-cabinet</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 22 Mar 2025 17:17:26 GMT</pubDate>
